<paragraph blockId="3.[806,1421,508,591]" pageId="3" pageNumber="537">
The name of the genus, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="PERIS, DAVIS ET DELCLOS" authorityYear="2014" box="[1077,1129,539,560]" class="Insecta" family="Nemonychidae" genus="Arra" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="537" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1077,1129,539,560]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="537">Arra</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, is Latin for ‘deposit’, and is treated as feminine in gender.
</paragraph>
